cu.explanation_en: GNB_PORT_FOR_X2C changed from 36422 to 70000, which exceeds the valid port range, causing X2-C interface binding failures and preventing CU-DU communication.
cu.explanation_zh: GNB_PORT_FOR_X2C 从 36422 更改为 70000，超过有效端口范围，导致 X2-C 接口绑定失败，阻止 CU-DU 通信。

du.explanation_en: absoluteFrequencySSB changed from 641280 to 0, which is below the valid frequency range, causing SSB frequency misalignment and cell synchronization failures.
du.explanation_zh: absoluteFrequencySSB 从 641280 更改为 0，低于有效频率范围，导致 SSB 频率错位和小区同步失败。
